            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tlahtolli nahuatl tlen quimanextia iixco tlacayoliztli tlen macehualli, quimanextia nochi tlen iixco quence tzontecomitl huan tlen toquechtlan.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Eastern Huasteca Nahuatl</Note_Language>
